reviewText: The content is identical to one called Ricky Nelson In Concert I bought from Amazon.co.uk and the quality is very poor, probably transferred unprofessionally from VHS. Most is from Live In Chicago, the rest very low quality O&H performances. The last number which would be something new is nonexistent. In short bootleg crap.

Please help me on this one. Its a DVD and it will not work in my DVD player nor my Computer. What do I do? Please help me for I paid alot for this. Shirley Cooper  I LOVE AMAZON I GOT MY MONEY BACK ON THIS BECAUSE IT HAD NOTHING ON IT. I LOVE RICKY NELSON HE WAS AS GOOD OR BETTER THAN ELVIS. I DO HOPE THIS DVD COMES BACK TO AMAZON. BLESS AMAZON.
